<div>
  <h1>Too Cool to Use Regular Ipsum?</h1>

  <h2>add some trendiness to your ipsum</h2>

  <p>To generate your <b>hipsum</b>, fill out the form below.</p>

  <ul>
    <li>For paragraphs use a number (default is 5)</li>
    <li>For sentences use a number</li>
    <li>ONLY ONE CAN BE USED</li>
  </ul>
</div>

<div class="form_section">
  <form action="/hipster_result">
    <div>
      <label for="num_para">Number of paragraphs: </label>
      <input type="text" id="num_para" name="paragraph" placeholder="5" size="2">
    </div>

    <div>
      <p>OR</p>
    </div>

    <div>
      <label for="num_sent">Number of sentences: </label>
      <input type="text" id="num_sent" name="sentence" placeholder="4" size="2">
    </div>

    <div>
      <button><a href="#"></a>Get Your Hipsum!</a></button>
    </div>

  </form>
</div>
